+# Free access signup codes
+
+Some ArtsFolio invitations include a free access signup code. When you enter one of these codes, the signup form lets you choose a plan and shows how many months of free access are included.
+
+After the free access period ends, your selected plan remains the tenant's plan, but platform billing may apply according to the current ArtsFolio billing setup.
